text: Innertkirchen is a municipality in the administrative district of Interlaken- Oberhasli in the canton of Bern in Switzerland. On 1 January 2014, the former municipality of Gadmen merged into the municipality of Innertkirchen. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website of Innertkirchen Category:Municipalities in Interlaken-Oberhasli
